      • setupCheckBox

        private static void setupCheckBox​(javafx.scene.control.CheckBox box,
                                  Property property)
        Does a one way binding of a CheckBox to a Property. Initially sets the value of the CheckBox according to the Properties value. As soon as the CheckBox value changes, the Property value will also change.
        Parameters:
        box - the CheckBox to be set up
        property - the Property that will be bound to the CheckBox
